| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6894 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6a3d4116-b9eb-5bf3-a3af-8e267f46ffaa"
